        <b><h3 style=" color: rgb(13, 103, 82);">Construction and Inauguaration</h3></b>
        <p class="inauguration">The construction of the <i><b>Hijagang</b></i> watercraft storage building started in the year 2010 and completed in the year 2013.
        On 21 August 2013, with the performances of necessary religious rites and rituals by the <b><i>Amaibas</i></b>(Meitei for <b><i>'priests'</i></b>) and the <i><b>Amaibis</b></i>
        (Meitei for <i><b>'priestesses'</b></i>) in the early morning, the Hijagang was inaugurated by <i><b>Okram Ibobi Singh</b></i>, the then Chief Minister of Manipur, 
        who was also the then President of <b>"Kangla Fort Board"</b></p>
  </div>
